title: Carnival Cruise Terminal
description:
Carnival Cruise Lines. Carnival Journeys cruises go to great destinations, with enriching experiences, classic cruising flair and more on the way.
tel:(305) 406-5437
http://www.carnival.com/

title: Garage G
description:
Parking is conveniently available at all cruise terminals. Designated disabled permit parking spaces are available in each garage. Spaces are also available for oversized vehicles (oversized vans, recreational vehicles and vehicles with trailers) at special rates. All facilities are patrolled by security. Oversized vehicles may only park in Lot #2, across from Cruise Terminal E.
For more information visit:
http://www.miamidade.gov

title: Trolley Stop
description:
There are two Miami Trolley stops at the Port. Please make a note of the destinations at each stop: Port Miami North stop: Terminal B, Terminal C, Terminal D, Terminal E, Terminal F, Terminal G, Terminal H, Port Miami Administrative Building, Port Miami Garage Port Miami South stop: Terminal J, Royal Caribbean Corporate Office.
For more information visit:
http://www.miamidade.gov
